DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(3,7,1);
$coef2 =  2*$a1*$a1;
$coef0 = random(1,11,1);
$e1 = -$a1+1;
$d1 = 2*$a1+1;
##min at $b1
##max at -$a1
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Consider the function \( f(x) = x^4 - $coef2 x^2  + $coef0, \quad
 $e1 \leq x \leq $d1 \).
This function has an absolute minimum value equal to \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR
EOT
$ans = $a1**4 - $coef2*$a1**2  + $coef0;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and an absolute maximum value equal to \{ans_rule(20) \}
EOT
$ans = $d1**4 - $coef2*$d1**2  + $coef0;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

